Luma Home Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 25, 2017 11:06 PM ET
Communications Equipment

Company Overview of Luma Home Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Luma Home Inc. designs and manufactures Wi-Fi routers for household network. It also offers power cords and cables, wireless router cords, wireless routers. The company is headquartered in Atlanta, Georgia.


75 5th Street NWSuite 208Atlanta, GA 30308United States



Phone: 800-684-5862

